Are you prepared?

25
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,360
Yes, I am.

26
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:17,080
Ms. Hua. Take a look at this letter.

27
00:02:17,190 --> 00:02:18,000
This fan wrote,

28
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,150
dear Jingxi,

29
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,760
since fans call themselves watermelons,

30
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,030
whenever I eat watermelon,

31
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:24,000
I feel I’m eating another one
of your fans.

32
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,960
So to live up to their sacrifice,

33
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:31,190
I invented various ways to
eat watermelons.

34
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,520
Watermelon sashimi. Watermelon broth.

35
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,470
Watermelon salad.

36
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,030
These show my fans’ love for me.

37
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,870
I need to reply to all of them.

38
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,520
Why don’t we host an event
to express your gratitude?

39
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,630
Don’t rush to disagree.

40
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:48,310
Look.

41
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,520
This incident changed

42
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:52,400
so many people’s views about you.

43
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,750
At this point,

44
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,400
your attitude is important.

45
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,840
Let’s host a return banquet to

46
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:59,080
show the fans that you care about them.

47
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,520
But isn’t it better if

48
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,400
I reply to their letters personally?

49
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,630
Besides,

50
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,000
throwing a return banquet now
may make people feel that

51
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,360
I’m taking advantage of the event

52
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:09,630
to gain attention and advertise myself.

53
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,520
I don’t like it.

54
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:12,400
Well.

55
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:15,000
You have good intentions,
while my eyes are on money.

56
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,310
All I want is to help you gain more fans

57
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,750
and get more popular.

58
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,430
Ms. Hua.

59
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,560
I know you only want what’s good for me.

60
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,710
But after this incident,

61
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,840
I start to realize that

62
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:32,120
I’m not worthy of their affection.

63
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:35,680
My fans support me unreservedly.

64
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,590
I should work harder too.

65
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:40,800
Yuan.

66
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,030
Ning Zeyu.

67
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:42,750
Li He.

68
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:45,190
They are all pursuing their dreams.

69
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,030
So, I think...

70
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,710
Me.

71
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,590
The popular idol, Ye Jingxi

72
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,360
will study from today on.

73
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,560
I’ll prepare for College Entrance Exam.

74
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:57,000
And I’ll prepare for
the music major’s test.

75
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,240
I’ll get into
Haixing Conservatory of Music

76
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,870
and become a professional music producer

77
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,150
to repay their affection.

78
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,680
Actually,

79
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,430
you can consider

80
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:10,240
studying abroad.

81
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,360
Haixing Conservatory of Music
is a good school.

82
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,630
But its courses are more about
classic music theories.

83
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:17,510
I don’t think
that’s the right school for you.

84
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,120
Look.

85
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:23,120
This is the school I asked them
to investigate.

86
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,510
Austria Lakeside Music School.

87
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:28,310
I think this is the right school for you
considering all the factors.

88
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:29,950
Ms. Hua.

89
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,000
I know.

90
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:33,120
You don’t want to part
with your friends.

91
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,430
But, Jingxi.

92
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:36,680
Like what you’ve just said,

93
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:40,120
your friends are all
fighting for their dreams.

94
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,870
They should be your source of power.

95
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,870
I wish you can make the decision

96
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:48,040
after you’ve thought about it carefully.

97
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,630
In this case, you won’t have regrets.

98
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:53,950
Fine.

99
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,430
Think about it first.

100
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:56,360
-Okay.
-I’ll go for now.

101
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,310
Let me walk you out.

102
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,070
Ms. Hua, bye.

103
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,270
Take care.

104
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:19,360
You wish to be a better self
for your friends and fans.

105
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,630
Then, you must aspire higher.

106
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,160
Find the career that’s suitable for you.

107
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,480
Real friendships

108
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,830
