161
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,000
But you’re still so handsome.

162
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:46,160
You still have so many fans.

163
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,120
No wonder he’s my idol.

164
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,870
Do you know that

165
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,800
I wrote an anonymous fan letter?

166
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,950
Anonymous?

167
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:54,480
Yes, I get to see Jingxi every day.

168
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,870
If he knows it’s me, it’ll be awkward.

169
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:58,870
Wow, Han Yayi,
does Lin Chuan know what you did?

170
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:00,830
-He can only know from you.
-Caixi.

171
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,870
-Good morning.
-Yuan.

172
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:05,870
Caixi, now’s the new semester.

173
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:07,040
I’ll be No.1 again.

174
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:10,070
I won’t let that happen.

175
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,830
Can we have a better chat
at the beginning of the semester?

176
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,720
Caixi, in this new semester,

177
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,600
I’ll protect you.

178
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,360
Yuan.

179
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,750
Yes.

180
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:26,310
Nothing. It’s just great
to see you again.

181
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,430
We see each other every day.

182
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,870
Can you let me copy
your math homework?

183
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,840
I have English homework.
Do you want that?

184
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,030
Ah. Give me your English homework.

185
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,910
I can lend it to you.
But you have to promise me.

186
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,270
You’ll never copy my homework again.

187
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,960
Chuan, you’re so mean.

188
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,550
I’ll tell Han Yayi that you like her.

189
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:44,720
Dare you threaten me!

190
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,910
Here. Take it.

191
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:48,000
Just my homework.

192
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,790
How dare you

193
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,120
tell Han Yayi!

194
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:54,150
You had a better one than me.
My mom hired a tutor for me.

195
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:56,000
I had five hours’ classes every day.

196
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,320
Where have you been
in the winter vocation?

197
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:00,480
My mom and dad took me to Heihujiang.

198
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,030
That’s the first time I saw snow.

199
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:04,840
Zeyu.

200
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,910
Have you done your English homework?

201
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,080
I want to check my answer with you.

202
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,750
I don’t have to do that.

203
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,000
Good morning.

204
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,670
Stand up.

205
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:18,510
-Good morning, teacher.
-Good morning, teacher.

206
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,550
Sit down please.

207
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,200
Today is the first day of this semester.

208
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,360
I have something to tell you.

209
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:30,870
Pan Hao has transferred
to another school.

210
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,910
I won’t elaborate on the reasons.

211
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,080
But I have to warn you.

212
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:40,200
There is less than half of a year left
before the college entrance exam.

213
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:43,480
Your future is a new start
that’s full of hope.

214
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,720
It’s also a start of hard work.

215
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,790
The next few months are very important.

216
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:51,080
So I wish you can put
aside the things that

217
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,240
aren’t related
to the college entrance exam.

218
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:55,870
These few months pass by so quickly.

219
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:58,720
Let’s all bite the bullet and work hard.

220
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,440
Okay?

221
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,000
Yes.

222
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:06,790
Let’s open the book.

223
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:10,240
Page 49.

224
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,240
Read the poem with me.

225
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:16,380
(Class 2, Grade 3)

226
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,200
You’re looking for me?

227
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,840
Another gossip?

228
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,720
Someone tipped you off again?

229
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,150
They’re investigating my identity again?

230
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:37,240
No.

231
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,000
This incident is over now.

232
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,910
Stop thinking about all day.

233
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:41,550
It’s fine.

234
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:45,150
Why are you being so mysterious then?

235
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,790
Yuan.

236
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,000
I have a question for you.

237
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:54,030
Answer it truthfully.

238
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,440
Listen.

239
00:10:57,870 --> 00:11:00,080
If you have the chance to go abroad now,

240
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:02,320
will you go?

241
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,440
Go abroad?

242
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:09,790
I’ve never thought about it.

243
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,910
Besides, I’ll have college entrance exam
next semester.

244
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,510
I don’t want to go.

245
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,960
If you can study abroad?

246
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,360
Study abroad?

247
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,870
That’s even less possible.

248
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,480
You know that my family situation
won’t allow that.

249
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:24,360
Besides, I’d be worried if I leave
my mom and brother behind.

250
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,440
If you can set those aside?

251
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,600
If you don’t have to think about others?

252
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,550
Just ask yourself.

253
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,720
Do you want to go?

254
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,670
I’ve never thought about that.

255
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:49,840
Then think carefully.

256
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,240
Tell me when you’ve made the decision.

257
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,600
Wow.

258
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:56,750
Wait a second.

259
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,870
Why are you being so weird today?

260
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,550
If you don’t know where to go,
you can check on the European schools.

261
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,840
There are many good
finance colleges in Europe.

262
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:11,840
You can do some research.

263
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,200
Think about it.

264
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,870
Europe?

265
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,750
The fifteenth Haiwen
Junior Championships.

266
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:36,150
I don’t have to reiterate
the importance of this match, right?

267
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,440
This is city level competitions.

268
00:12:37,670 --> 00:12:38,870
The preliminaries will be hosted
next week.

269
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,270
If you have good performance,

270
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:42,670
get into the final, and get into top 3,

271
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,720
you can apply for
national second level athlete.

272
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,320
Yes.

273
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,840
If you become
national second level athlete,

274
