338
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,510
Why?

339
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,870
Which race champion is from Africa?

340
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,840
Kenmerick.

341
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:18,270
You’re indeed crazy about running.

342
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:19,630
Yes.

343
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:21,390
When I’m running,

344
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,480
