347
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:32,750
Oh.

348
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:35,960
Yuan Caixi.

349
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:43,000
Can you run with me?

350
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:50,080
But I can’t run fast.

351
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,270
I can carry you on my back

352
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:57,910
