357
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:11,880
What are you doing?

358
00:17:15,330 --> 00:17:16,810
♪Please listen♪

359
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:18,310
Where are you going?

360
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:19,640
Don’t mind me.

361
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,400
Let me open it myself.

362
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,240
Aren’t you going to try it?

363
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,400
Let me try it myself.

364
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,110
Let me open it for you, then.

365
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:23,680
No need.

366
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,070
Hurry up.

367
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,510
My dad is really good at cooking.

368
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:32,010
