373
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:41,680
Caixi.

374
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:42,590
Mom.

375
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:45,480
You’re willing to come back?

376
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,350
Am I talking to you?

377
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,640
What are you looking at?

378
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:49,030
Mrs. Yuan is talking about

379
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:51,960
