380
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,310
Oh my god.

381
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,920
This photo must be over 20 years old.

382
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,830
This is from 18 years ago.

383
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,200
This is my favorite one.

384
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:05,750
We just got married at that time.

385
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,110
Now I look back on that time.

386
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,720
We were so poor back then.

387
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,550
I originally told him that

388
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:18,350
