389
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,750
But you dad just didn’t agree.

390
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:22,750
He insisted on taking me
to another country.

391
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,640
I was really so worried.

392
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:28,400
