395
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:33,960
Why?

396
00:18:34,110 --> 00:18:34,720
Well.

397
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:36,790
It was so cheap.

398
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:41,510
We spent five days in Thailand.

399
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:45,030
We spent too much time
in the swimming pool.

400
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,680
But we still didn’t wanna leave.

401
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:53,000
We just enjoyed food every day.

402
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,510
We had fun.

403
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:56,110
We wandered around.

404
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:59,200
It was such an amazing experience.

405
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:01,000
I was so happy.

406
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:05,200
Why didn’t we get married earlier?

407
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:10,270
Mom.

408
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,400
Do you want to visit Thailand again?

409
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:16,750
No.

410
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:17,920
Why?

411
00:19:21,350 --> 00:19:22,790
Because I’ve already seen

412
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,270
