424
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,680
You’ll know when you see it.

425
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,720
I’ve made the decision.

426
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,750
I’ll take my chance.

427
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:34,960
Ah?

428
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:38,790
I’ll go now.

