432
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:48,820
(File)

433
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:49,620
(Jingxi, our beloved idol)

434
00:20:49,620 --> 00:20:54,940
(Jingxi, our beloved idol
Concert The Crazy Night)

435
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:57,240
