438
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:05,000
I want to take the leap of faith
for myself.

439
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,000
I’ll host the return banquet.

440
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:09,030
And I’ll take this chance to tell Yuan

441
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,000
