you’re so conceited?

481
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:15,440
Yuan.

482
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:17,750
You must come.

483
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:22,640
But, Bear,

484
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:26,440
